  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc3\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dda \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dda \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dd4 \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0dd9\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0db1\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The search stops after the elephant crashes into Jackson's car",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Director General of Wildlife MGC Suriyabandara said that the search operation for the wild elephant that caused the accident of veteran actor Jackson Anthony was stopped.",
        "He mentioned that even though the wildlife officials have been searching for weeks to find the wild elephant, they have not been able to find it.",
        "Mr. Suriyabandara also said that the activities were stopped as it would be difficult to investigate further in practice.",
        "The Director General of Wildlife said that it is possible that the elephant was not seriously injured in the accident and that is why it was not found in that area.",
        "Mr. Suriyabandara said that hundreds of wildlife officials have checked the roads and areas where elephants roam to find the wild elephant and they have informed that they saw the wild elephant going to a distant forest area.",
        "The wildlife officials sought details about this elephant as per a request made by the police investigating the accident.",
        "A car carrying veteran actor Mr. Jackson Anthony and a group of others was hit by a wild elephant in Talawa area of \u200b\u200bAnuradhapura. Mr. Anthony sustained serious injuries and is still receiving treatment at the Colombo National Hospital."
      ],
